<br>
I use 1hs when EXPing and a 2hs when tanking..<br>
<br>
The Frostreaver for me has been one of the most reliable middle end game weapons i have.<br>
<br>
On the Low end the Stone Bladed Axe of Dismay has worked well.<br>
<br>
Here is the Key Point, &quot;YOU MUST HAVE HASTE FOR 2HS TO BE EFFECTIVE&quot;<br>
<br>
RBB + VOG works well<br>
or COF + VOG<br>
<br>
That combind with the high frequency of procs from the frost reaver tend to work really well.<br>
